01:16.456 --> 01:29.234
In this episode of Light and Truth, John Piper takes us beneath the surface of John 3 16 to show that the foundation of our salvation is God's passion for His own name.

01:30.018 --> 01:36.548
The seminar was originally delivered at Bethlehem Baptist Church on Wednesday evening, November 13, 1991.

