03:56.290 --> 04:01.497
when I deal with you for my namesake and not according to your evil ways.

04:01.517 --> 04:20.403
So when I pray now on the basis of this verse, I have not only the mercy of God in general to plead over against my sins, I have the name of God to plead.

04:21.644 --> 04:25.970
And when you plead the name of God, that's what this lesson is all about tonight,

04:26.658 --> 04:31.003
you plead what he puts most story in.

04:32.224 --> 04:36.689
And so there is a tremendous argument that you can make with God.

04:36.710 --> 04:42.076
Spurgeon preached a great sermon one time about arguing with God.

04:42.476 --> 04:45.660
He said, we should be like lawyers when we come before God.

04:46.301 --> 04:54.610
Humble lawyers, but lawyers who make a case with God for why he should grant us the blessings we ask for.

04:54.978 --> 05:04.367
And so I want to stick into your lawyer's portfolio tonight an argument that God can't resist.

05:06.209 --> 05:08.171
Namely his name.

05:10.513 --> 05:24.306
You shall know that I am the Lord when I deal with you Bethlehem or John for my namesake and not according to your evil ways.

05:25.506 --> 05:34.635
There is a way to be saved even though we have evil ways, and that is to bank on the name of God.

05:35.816 --> 05:36.357
Let's pray.

05:39.380 --> 05:53.554
Father, I pray that far more than a mere intellectual grasp of this great truth tonight, though I ask for that, I ask for a profound

05:54.434 --> 06:21.042
spiritual appropriation in the very depths of our emotions that you love your name above all things, that you want to make a name for yourself and be famous in the world and that your passion to become famous and to preserve the glory and the honor and integrity of your name is paramount in your goals.

06:21.890 --> 06:35.911
And therefore, if we can kick in with that goal, if we can hide ourselves in that goal, if we can somehow clamp on to that goal, we are home, we are with you, and we are on the winning side.

06:36.192 --> 06:39.416
We will not be treated according to our evil ways anymore.

06:40.678 --> 06:44.364
We will be justified, and we will be glorified.

06:44.784 --> 06:51.154
I just pray earnestly that this take hold of us tonight, Father, that your great

06:51.682 --> 07:02.574
Awesome, incomprehensible, energetic zeal for your name would become the foundation of our hope.

07:06.638 --> 07:09.301
In Jesus' name is name, I pray.

07:10.122 --> 07:10.482
Amen.

