08:21.410 --> 08:50.962
if I used fame, and lo and behold, as I studied the meaning of the name of God in the Old Testament especially, it came clear that it not only was kind of a summary way of referring to his character, like if some, when you say that you do something for God's namesake, he leads us in paths of righteousness for his namesake.

08:51.458 --> 08:56.885
