09:36.921 --> 09:45.874
He has a character that's good and people know about the character therefore his reputation is good and you sum that all up with name, good name.

09:45.914 --> 09:48.818
And I think throughout the Bible,

09:49.122 --> 09:57.370
more often than not when God's name is talked about it has that public reputation idea to it.

09:57.950 --> 10:01.053
