10:01.093 --> 10:05.017
This is a chapter about God's reputation.

10:05.938 --> 10:18.290
God's love for his reputation, his pleasure in his reputation and therefore I chose the word fame instead of name and we'll see some biblical reasons

10:18.626 --> 10:22.270
