Take away my sins.

12:43.460 --> 12:44.882
Guard me from Satan.

12:44.994 --> 12:48.439
They're all in the same grammatical category of request.

12:49.842 --> 12:59.818
Now, if you think about that then and go back up to hallowed be your name, this is a tremendous way to structure your prayer life and to begin your prayers.

13:01.320 --> 13:12.658
