your name, your reputation to spread, cause me, my family, my church, I generally pray in concentric circles like that, cause me, Noel and Carson and Benjamin Abraham and Barnumus and the elders and the staff at Bethlehem and all the people at Bethlehem and this city and this state and the BGC and all the evangelical movement and the whole world that names you and those that don't hallow your name.

