I don't always get that far, but

13:41.378 --> 13:44.963
If I were to finish it all, that would be the way I would pray.

13:45.624 --> 13:50.491
We want your name to be known, loved, cherished, honored, praised.

13:52.875 --> 13:55.559
I heard Russ pray and sort of like that when we began tonight.

13:55.579 --> 13:58.924
He was using those kinds of words about the name of God.

