15:04.757 --> 15:05.778
That's our goal in life.

15:05.818 --> 15:07.100
That's the goal of foreign missions.

15:07.140 --> 15:08.062
That's the goal of prayer.

15:08.282 --> 15:09.224
That's the goal of preaching.

15:09.264 --> 15:10.646
