21:04.708 --> 21:09.373
This massive biblical foundation for the gospel.

21:10.734 --> 21:20.824
Generally, we simply start with John 3, 16, for God so loved the world that he sent his own son that anybody who believes in him might not perish, but have eternal life.

21:21.044 --> 21:23.186
